{"tid":1532464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[家長] 我要表揚下我老豆","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:54:37.000Z","uid":235484,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a161a93ee451a852125d6dddd19be09227b062aa","tid":1532464,"uid":235484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"老豆要長期喺大陸做嘢，今次反送中都冇乜點表過態，但係細個果陣佢俾過一疊六四剪報我睇，一直都覺得佢係淺黃<br />\n<br />\n直至琴晚機場一役⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：老豆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你睇下，機場啲人要行出市區，條路勁塞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我知啦，咁多人入去接放學<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩，你知咩係接放學?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點會唔知，我有follow立場架，你上tg睇下有冇人要接放學啦，我地一陣出車入去 (我要跟埋車因為我老豆冇tg )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAbvojs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAbvojs.jpg&h=128210e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺車度塞緊入去果陣，老豆同我講左好多睇法，831佢見到黑警喺太子站無差別攻擊覺得好嬲，令佢呢淺黃都要企出嚟 (等我開始遊說佢出嚟遊行先)<br />\n<br />\n民意一直都喺我地呢邊架手足們，我覺得個天枰會嚟越向我地靠攏，堅持一定會勝利！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bb0b52ecf3aca506573208339af336906053f6ad","tid":1532464,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ced91e6507f0f5886a374ccd90eec0bfb0943a4","tid":1532464,"uid":276758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi